added: Based in the hustle and bustle of a modern-day metropolis, three gods reward Shen Te's hospitality with a life-changing sum of money. With this sum she opens a tobacco shop and claims the stability she’s always dreamed of. However, forced to question the cost of her own survival, she resorts to scheming and deceit to flourish in this capitalist world.
